Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出米莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除武装后投降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, {\fnArial}Distraction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全无音航行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连气流噪声都听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦与格拉齐埃斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 准备作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的目标是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能将你们也卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我交出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为… 为何要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那复兴图兰的壮志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这点程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要有将我们作为垫脚石的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我牺牲是挺美好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不等于是对国民的背叛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我认为就算交出你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也不会放过这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 准备作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬… 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4号 挂装完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 人手换到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹种穿甲 距离20
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柯拜托 我也要出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里轮不到外行人上场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们把敌人引来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕后就出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我… 负起责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给我们这些专业的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我们才会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈判失败了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始射击
