Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕鲸…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 捕鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我一定完成契约
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是最好的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中没有回收你的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己回来吧
