Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标下降 开始潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军 避开了鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把他们轰出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 准备对潜战
