Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退路被断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方是悬崖 舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离到达悬崖 4000
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓经验的差距吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 一个坏消息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜舰长笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 舰长有重要的话要讲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塔琪安娜·魏斯洛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦要求我们交出受我舰保护中的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图兰流亡政府君主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 米莉亚·伊尔·维尔克·科托雷托拉·图兰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相应的 会保证我舰从此区域安全脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不过是联邦的诡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明显 他们的目标也包括捕获西尔维厄斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若本舰被捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给安纳托雷带来危机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需惧怕敌人的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不损一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员一起返回安纳托雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离相撞3500
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西丽 找出岩壁脆弱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左前方15度 距离3020
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现岩壁脆弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰首 多联装穿甲火箭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹种 尾翼脱壳弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开云层了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有投降信号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给全舰下达炮击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚 节流阀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尔维厄斯没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会让你自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算撞上也要把他们挡下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方有联邦舰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15秒后接触
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大输出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大输出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们当作跳板飞过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自毁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连碎片都不准备留给我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是… 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 到底打中什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国境附近的山岳好像崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四 第五编队多舰受损
