Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去确认西尔维厄斯有否沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
